{"tid":489704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好憎軟硬天師？","createTime":"2017-12-05T02:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T05:48:15.000Z","uid":70596,"like":18,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9930f6317d2c8d810c2b84a3609b5b0d32381026","tid":489704,"uid":70596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:48:49.000Z","msg":"先唔講九十年代啲歌好唔好聽有無內容，由細到大成日見到兩條友扮幽默風趣已經覺得好無聊。尤其係葛民輝，成五十歲人都仲懶調皮鬼馬，但唔知點解啲人咁鍾意搵佢拍廣告。<br />\n<br />\n我知一定有好多七八十後屌鳩我，因為呢兩條友響呢班人心目中已經上咗神台。"},{"pid":"63f420c569e50d78c3373a448abfe68d1e764c40","tid":489704,"uid":70596,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:50:28.000Z","msg":"話咁快就有一個負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0800ee7888e871d5540b4437476d786ca0bd5d3d","tid":489704,"uid":68367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"人地靠扮小丑揾食，算啦。<br />\n就好似伊麵咁，幾十歲人仲要扮MK。"},{"pid":"0815273f1730f0e8b97edf7fcd35a688dbb8d719","tid":489704,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:56:31.000Z","msg":"人地有market<br />\n但係唔包括你咁解姐<br />\n有咩好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acab85e343e87109303b858fd95a3c00ea4c1712","tid":489704,"uid":109983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1237f203dddd7e3cb3bda7db2b98bb8d17893329","tid":489704,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一隻小學雞留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e678363c633aaa78e37ff615c67d636b7d7435","tid":489704,"uid":70596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有market<br />\n但係唔包括你咁解姐<br />\n有咩好屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意，尤其係而家啲機構掌權果班都係六七十後多，我只不過想知連登咁多後生仔女，會唔會同我嘅諗法一致。"},{"pid":"cdc7a62b9b408e6f5218ffe7c99884aa6346df59","tid":489704,"uid":109983,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:12:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一隻小學雞留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死廢老一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d15701a758f792abbb11961dcdfd494feec62f","tid":489704,"uid":427,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>聽都未聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一隻小學雞留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死廢老一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n挑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eae2c1f3cc011dccb342f3c587555c28d34324","tid":489704,"uid":56013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"葛民輝，成五十歲人都仲懶調皮鬼馬<br />\n<br />\n呢下我真係好認同. 成日諗吊你扮咩後生呀撚樣."},{"pid":"fcc1434be0bf239a04061fd70594a876